title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 18 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 18 2022
description:
The return of covidiots. Clay thinks Dr. Fauci will "skate," but both Clay and Buck think there should be hearings, Buck says, "into the damage that was done by his willingness to lie." Buck stressed, "I think Fauci should be thought of as the biomedical equivalent of a war criminal." Dr. Ashish Jha, White House Coronavirus Response Coordinator, pushes for more worthless indoor mask mandates. Courageous L.A. doctors speak the truth on covid. L.A. County + USC Chief Medical Officer Brad Spellberg: "This isn’t the same pandemic that it was, despite media hype to the contrary." Fauci says he plans to retire by the time Biden’s current term ends in January, 2025. MSNBC’s Katy Tur: "People don't trust us -- they don’t believe us." C&B agree.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
